输入：
Logs 表：
+----+-----+
| id | num |
+----+-----+
| 1  | 1   |
| 2  | 1   |
| 3  | 1   |
| 4  | 2   |
| 5  | 1   |
| 6  | 2   |
| 7  | 2   |
+----+-----+
输出：
Result 表：
+-----------------+
| ConsecutiveNums |
+-----------------+
| 1               |
+-----------------+
解释：1 是唯一连续出现至少三次的数字。

SELECT DISTINCT a.num AS ConsecutiveNums FROM Logs a
JOIN Logs b ON b.id = a.id+1
JOIN Logs c ON c.id = a.id+2
WHERE a.num = b.num AND a.num = c.num;
